Drivetrain Controls:
Left joystick up/down: Move forward/backward
Left joystick left/right: Move left/right
Right joystick left/right: Turn left/right
Right bumper: Drive slow


Arm Controls:
Left joystick up/down: Arm tilt up/down
Right joystick up/down: Viper Slides extend/retract
A button: Arm Tilts slow
B button: Arm Tilts fast
X button: Viper Slides fast